\c 15
\s Abhusaromu anomukira baba vake Dhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika shure kweizvi kuti Abhusaromu wakazvigadzirira ngoro nemabhiza nevarume makumi mashanu vachimhanya mberi kwake\x + 1 Madz. 1.5.\x*.
\v 2 Abhusaromu ndokumuka mangwanani, ndokumira parutivi rwenzira yesuwo; zvino zvakaitika, kana munhu upi neupi akava nemhosva yemurairo waiuya kuna mambo kuzotongwa, ipapo Abhusaromu waimudana ndokuti: Uri weguta ripi? Kana akati: Muranda wenyu ndewerimwe rwemarudzi aIsraeri;
\v 3 zvino Abhusaromu waiti kwaari: Ona, nyaya yako yakanaka uye yakarurama, asi hakuna wamambo kuti akunzwe.
\v 4 Abhusaromu waitiwo: Dai ndaiva ndaiswa kuva mutongi panyika, kuti ani nani ane mhosva yemurairo kana nyaya auye kwandiri, zvino ndaimururamisira\x + Vato. 9.29.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino zvakaitika paiswedera munhu kumukotamira, kuti waitandavadza ruoko rwake, ndokumubata, ndokumutsvoda.
\v 6 Zvino Abhusaromu waiita nenzira iyi kuna Israeri wose waiuya kuna mambo kuzotongwa; naizvozvo Abhusaromu wakatapa moyo yevarume vekwaIsraeri.
\p
\v 7 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwemakore makumi mana, kuti Abhusaromu wakati kuna mambo: Nditenderei henyu ndiende ndindoripira mhiko yangu yandakapikira Jehovha kuHebhuroni\x + 1 Sam. 16.1.\x*.
\v 8 Nokuti muranda wenyu wakapika mhiko\x + Gen.. 28.20,21.\x* pandaiva ndichigere paGeshuri muSiriya, ndichiti: Kana Jehovha akandidzosera zvekundidzosera kuJerusarema, zvino ndichashumira Jehovha\x + 13.38.\x*.
\v 9 Mambo ndokuti kwaari: Enda nerugare. Zvino wakasimuka ndokuenda kuHebhuroni\x + 1 Sam. 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Asi Abhusaromu wakatuma vashori mumarudzi ose aIsraeri achiti: Pamunongonzwa kurira kwehwamanda, ipapo muchati: Abhusaromu ndimambo paHebhuroni.
\v 11 Zvino kwakaenda pamwe naAbhusaromu varume mazana maviri kubva muJerusarema, vakakokwa\x + 1 Sam. 9.13. 1 Sam. 16.3,5.\x*; ivo ndokuenda muchokwadi chavo uye vasingazivi chinhu chipi nechipi\x + Gen.. 20.5. 1 Madz. 22.34.\x*.
\v 12 Abhusaromu ndokutuma \add nhume\add* kuno\add dana\add* Ahitoferi muGironi\x + 15.31. 16.20. 17.1,14,23. 11.3. 23.34.\x* gurukota raDhavhidhi\x + 1 Makor. 27.33. Map. 41.9. 55.12,13,14.\x* kubva kuguta rake kubva muGiro\x + Josh. 15.51.\x*, paaibaira zvibairo. Bangano ndokusimba, uye vanhu vakaenda ndokuwanda\x + Map. 3.1.\x* kuna Abhusaromu\x + 3.1. Eki. 19.19.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Zvino kwakasvika nhume kuna Dhavhidhi ichiti: Moyo wevanhu vekwaIsraeri unotevera Abhusaromu\x + 15.6. Vato. 9.3.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati kuvaranda vake vose vaiva naye paJerusarema: Simukai, uye ngatitize, nokuti hatina mapukunyukiro pachiso chaAbhusaromu\x + 19.9. Map. 3.\x*; kurumidzai kuenda, zvimwe angakurumidza akatiwana ndokutiitira zvakaipa, nekurova guta nekwakapinza kwemunondo.
\v 15 Varanda vamambo ndokuti kuna mambo: Sezvose ishe wangu, mambo, zvaanosarudza, tarirai, varanda venyu \add vanoita\add*.
\v 16 Zvino mambo wakabuda, neimba yake yose iri patsoka dzake. Mambo ndokusiya vakadzi gumi varongo kuti vachengete imba\x + 16.21,22.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino mambo wakabuda, nevanhu vose vari patsoka dzake, ndokumira panzvimbo iri chinhambwe.
\v 18 Zvino varanda vake vose vakapfuura kurutivi rwake, nevaKereti\x + 1 Sam. 30.14.\x* vose, nevaPereti\x + 8.18.\x* vose, nevaGiti vose, varume mazana matanhatu vaiva vamutevera vachibva kuGati\x + 1 Sam. 27.2. 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, vakapfuura pamberi pamambo.
\p
\v 19 Mambo ndokuti kuna Itai muGiti\x + 18.2.\x*: Newe unoenderei nesu? Dzokera ugare namambo, nokuti iwe uri mutorwa uyewo uri mudzingwa kunzvimbo yako\x + 2 Madz. 17.23. 24.14. 25.21. Amo. 1.5. 6.7.\x*.
\v 20 Wakasvika zuro, zvino nhasi ndingakufambisa-fambisa nekuenda nesu, sezvandinoenda kwandinoenda? Dzokera udzosewo hama yako; nyasha nechokwadi ngazvive newe\x + 1 Sam. 23.13.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino Itai wakapindura mambo ndokuti: \add Na\add*Jehovha mupenyu, uye \add na\add*she wangu mambo mupenyu\x + Rut. 3.13. Rut. 1.16,17.\x*, zvirokwazvo panzvimbo iyo ishe wangu mambo pangava parufu kana paupenyu, muranda wenyu achava ipapowo.
\v 22 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kuna Itai: Enda uyambuke\x + 15.23.\x*. Itai muGiti ndokuyambuka, nevanhu vake vose, nevanana vose vaiva naye.
\v 23 Nyika yose ndokuchema nenzwi guru, uye vanhu vose vakayambuka; namambo wakayambuka rukova Kidhoroni\x + 1 Madz. 2.37. 15.13. 2 Madz. 23,4,6,12. 2 Makor. 15.16. 29.16. 30.14. Jer. 31.40.\x*, nevanhu vose vakayambuka nechekunzira yerenje\x + 15.28. 16.2. 17.16,29.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Zvino tarira, naZadhoki neVaRevhi vose vanaye\x + 8.17. 20.25. 1 Madz. 4.4.\x* vakatakura areka yesungano yaMwari\x + Num.. 4.15.\x*; vakaisa areka yaMwari pasi\x + Josh. 7.23.\x*, Abhiatari ndokukwira\x + 20.25. 1 Sam. 22.20. 23.6,9. 1 Madz. 4.4.\x*, kusvika vanhu vose vapera kupfuura vachibva muguta.
\v 25 Mambo ndokuti kuna Zadhoki: Dzoserai areka yaMwari muguta; kana ndikawana nyasha pameso aJehovha, achandidzosazve\x + Map. 43.3.\x* agondionesa iyo nenzvimbo yake yekugara\x + Eki. 15.13. Jer. 25.30.\x*.
\v 26 Asi kana achireva seizvi: Handifari newe\x + 22.20. Num.. 14.8. 1 Madz. 10.9. 2 Makor. 9.8. Map. 18.19. 22.8. Isa. 62.4.\x*; tarirai, ndiri \add pano\add*, ngaandiitire sezvakanaka pameso ake\x + Vato. 10.15.\x*.
\v 27 Mambo ndokuti kuna Zadhoki mupristi: Uri muoni here\x + 1 Sam. 9.9.\x*? Dzokera muguta nerugare, naAhimaazi mwanakomana wako, naJonatani mwanakomana waAbhiatari, vanakomana venyu vaviri pamwe nemwi\x + 15.36. 17.17. 18.19,27. 1 Madz. 1.42. 4.15. 1 Makor. 6.8,53.\x*.
\v 28 Ona, ndicharinda pamazambuko erenje, kusvika kwasvika shoko kubva kwamuri kundiudza\x + 2.29. 4.7. 17.16. Josh. 5.10. 18.18. 2 Madz. 25.4,5. Jer. 39.4,5. 52.7,8.\x*.
\v 29 Naizvozvo Zadhoki naAbhitari vakadzosera areka yaMwari Jerusarema; ivo vakagarapo.
\p
\v 30 Dhavhidhi ndokukwira nekumukwidza weMiorivhi, ndokuchema paaikwira, uye wakafukidza musoro wake\x + 19.4. Esi. 6.12. Jer. 14.3,4.\x*, ndokufamba asina shangu\x + Isa. 20.2,4.\x*; nevanhu vose vaiva naye vakafukidza umwe neumwe musoro wake, ndokukwira, vachikwira vachichema\x + 5.10. Map. 126.6.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Zvino kwakaudzwa Dhavhidhi zvichinzi: Ahitoferi ari pakati pebangano naAbhusaromu. Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Jehovha, itai henyu zano raAhitoferi\x + 16.23. 17.14,23.\x* rive upenzi.
\p
\v 32 Zvino zvakaitika kuti Dhavhidhi wakasvika pamusoro paainamata Mwari; uye tarira, Hushai muAriki wakasangana naye\x + Josh. 16.2.\x*, nguvo refu yake yakabvarurwa\x + 1.2.\x*, nevhu riri mumusoro wake\x + Josh. 7.6.\x*.
\v 33 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kwaari: Kana wopfuura neni, uchava mutoro kwandiri\x + 19.35.\x*.
\v 34 Asi kana ukadzokera kuguta, ukanoti kuna Abhusaromu: Ndichava muranda wenyu, mambo\x + 16.19.\x*; ini ndaiva muranda wababa venyu ipapo, ikozvinowo ini ndichava muranda wenyu; ipapo uchandiparadzira zano raAhitoferi\x + Map. 33.10.\x*.
\v 35 Uye havako here pamwe newe ipapo Zadhoki naAbhiatari vapristi? Naizvozvo kuchati nyaya yose yauchanzwa mumba mamambo, uchaiudza Zadhoki naAbhiatari vapristi\x + 17.15,16.\x*.
\v 36 Tarira, varipo ipapo pamwe navo vanakomana vavo vaviri, Ahimaazi waZadhoki, naJonatani waAbhiatari. Zvino uchatumira neruoko rwavo kwandiri chinhu chose chauchanzwa\x + 15.27.\x*.
\v 37 Zvino Hushai shamwari yaDhavhidhi wakasvika kuguta\x + 16.16. 1 Makor. 27.33. 1 Madz. 4.5,16.\x*; Abhusaromu ndokupinda muJerusarema\x + 16.15.\x*.